A good part of those tweeting expressed their indignation about these
practices, like [David Lopez Canales](https://twitter.com/Lopezydavid) and
[Diego Obiol](https://twitter.com/dobiol):

> [@Lopezydavid](https://twitter.com/TCAvendano/status/312589553766629378):
> [@TCAvendano](https://twitter.com/TCAvendano)[@elmundoes](https://twitter.com/elmundoes)
> y lo peor es que esto lo tienen todos los partidos. Y lo aún peor que hay
> ‘opinadores’ que llaman para pedirlo…

> [@Lopezydavid](https://twitter.com/TCAvendano/status/312589553766629378):
> [@TCAvendano](https://twitter.com/TCAvendano)[@elmundoes](https://twitter.com/elmundoes)
> and the worst thing is that all of the parties have this. And even worse is
> that there are ‘opinion-givers’ that ask to do it…

> [@dobiol](https://twitter.com/dobiol/status/312552376961732609): Lapsus-
> Mail, [#elconcepto](https://twitter.com/search?q=%23elconcepto&src=hash) y
> [#laevidencia](https://twitter.com/search?q=%23laevidencia&src=hash) > la
> maquinaria de des-información del PP nutrida de opinadores en nómina.

> [@dobiol](https://twitter.com/dobiol/status/312552376961732609): Lapsus
> Email, [#elconcepto](https://twitter.com/search?q=%23elconcepto&src=hash)
> and [#laevidencia](https://twitter.com/search?q=%23laevidencia&src=hash) >
> the dis-información machine of the PP fed by paid opinion-givers.

The website [Renovación
Balear.es](http://www.periodistadigital.com/renovacionbalear/mallorca/2013/03/15/el-
pp-mete-la-pata-y-confirma-por-error-la-noticia-de-rb-sobre-la-legion-de-
opinadores-que-intoxica-los-digitales.shtml) [es], which as was mentioned at
the beginning, was the first to denounce these practices on the islands,
ventures:

> Esta mala praxis, se deduce, se extiende por ende a todas las comunidades
> autónomas, y deja bien a las claras cómo se las gasta el partido y de qué
> forma se afana por controlar y manipular desde la sombra lo más elemental:
> el derecho a expresarse libremente sin interferencias ni distorsiones.

> This bad practice, it can be assumed, therefore extends to all the
> autonomous communities, and leaves quite clear how the party spends and how
> it makes an effort to control and manipulate from the sideline the most
> elemental thing: the right to express oneself freely and without
> interferences or distortions.

